stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Loading: mount(article)
    
    Loading --> Creating: article not exists
    Loading --> Editing: article exists
    
    Creating --> FormEntry
    Editing --> FormEntry
    
    FormEntry --> LanguageSwitch: Change selectedLanguage
    LanguageSwitch --> FormEntry
    
    FormEntry --> ImageUpload: Upload cover image
    ImageUpload --> ImagePreview: Valid image (jpeg/png/jpg/bmp)
    ImagePreview --> FormEntry
    ImageUpload --> FormEntry: Invalid image
    
    FormEntry --> StatusChange: Change status
    StatusChange --> Draft: Status = Draft
    StatusChange --> Published: Status = Published
    Draft --> FormEntry
    Published --> DateRequired: Require published_on
    DateRequired --> FormEntry
    
    FormEntry --> Validating: save()
    
    Validating --> SlugGeneration: slug empty
    SlugGeneration --> DateGeneration: Generate from title[en]
    Validating --> DateGeneration: slug exists
    
    DateGeneration --> Validation: published_on empty & status = Published
    DateGeneration --> Validation: Date set to today
    DateGeneration --> Validation: published_on exists
    
    Validation --> Saving: Validation Success
    Validation --> FormEntry: Validation Failed
    
    Saving --> MediaHandling: Save article
    MediaHandling --> ClearMedia: cover uploaded
    ClearMedia --> AddMedia: Clear existing cover
    AddMedia --> SuccessToast: Save to collection
    MediaHandling --> SuccessToast: No cover uploaded
    
    SuccessToast --> FormEntry: Update mode (stay on page)
    SuccessToast --> [*]: Create mode (redirect to edit)
    
    FormEntry --> [*]: Cancel (redirect to list)
    
    note right of FormEntry
        - Multi-language tabs (title, content)
        - Slug input with prefix
        - Status selection (Draft/Published)
        - Date picker for published_on
        - Image upload with preview
        - TinyMCE editor
    end note
    
    note right of Saving
